title: PSP2PS3 - Hysteria Project
description:
Hysteria Project

Language: English
PSN code: NPUZ00072

Step into the shoes of the main character and take part in an unforgettable adventure! 

Hysteria Project is a groundbreaking gaming experience, where you are the hero of an entirely filmed adventure. Go along with the video clips, keep a sharp eye on what's going on around you and most importantly of all - make the right choices at the right time.

This is an official PSP2PS3 converted image, just install the *.pkg file on your PS3. Should work on 4.2x+ CFW as a PSP miniS.
